            <description><![CDATA[【圆肩驼背没得救？6个动作帮你改善！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[加油]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_jiayou-a34ced0409.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】经常窝在沙发里、趴在桌子上刷手机，感觉颈肩酸痛，头痛头晕？这可能是得了上交叉综合征。试试这6个动作，预防和改善上交叉综合征！快马住，练起来！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E6%97%8F%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E9%A2%88%E8%82%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E6%97%8F%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E9%A2%88%E8%82%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#久坐族如何保护颈肩#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4940071770718226" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hhdkisotodj61o50xuawr02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/aaa2mnHOlx088bpdIjPy01041200PuNh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1693399079&amp;ssig=1Axpphm7ig&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/LQJA3Xb3lx088bpdrO4U01041200pAmM0E010.mp4?label=m